<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Love on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/love/</link><description>Recent content in Love on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Tue, 31 May 2011 13:13:18 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/love/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>爱一个人</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/love-someone/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 May 2011 13:13:18 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/love-someone/</guid><description>爱一个人，要了解、开解、道歉、道谢；认错改错；体贴体谅；接受不忍受；宽容不纵容；支持不支配；慰问不质问；倾诉不控诉。难忘而非遗忘，彼此交流而非凡事交代。默默祈求而非多要求。浪漫但勿浪费，牵手勿轻易放手。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/love-someone/featured.png"/></item><item><title>将爱情进行到底</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/eternal-moment/</link><pubDate>Tue, 15 Feb 2011 08:52:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/eternal-moment/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了作者在情人节时观看一部电影《将爱》并感到纠结和不适合。他希望能找到更温馨浪漫的电影来延续十年前的感动和纯真的感情。作者认为通过看别人的故事可以避免犯错，并表示自己珍爱生活和爱情。他希望自己的爱情能像电影中的情侣一样真挚和纯粹，而不需要被现实生活撕裂。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/eternal-moment/featured.png"/></item><item><title>情人节快乐</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/valentines-day/</link><pubDate>Mon, 14 Feb 2011 22:22:40 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/valentines-day/</guid><description>文章内容是关于情人节快乐的祝福和感谢，以及作者对爱、幸福和长久之情的表达。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/valentines-day/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>